{"tid":1053863,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【李東海小學老師墮樓亡】東華如果唔徹查林老師跳樓單嘢　以後叫你身邊親朋戚友咪撚捐錢！！！","createTime":"2019-03-09T11:40:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-19T23:32:14.000Z","uid":15229,"like":51,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c4523f882461719d1854c91fcdee60e6f0df8b58","tid":1053863,"uid":15229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T11:40:05.000Z","msg":"天水圍東華三院李東海小學林老師跳樓單嘢，愈爆愈多料！<br />\n個仆街校長劣行愈挖愈多，愈挖愈醜惡！<br />\n本人強烈要求教育局、東華三院徹底調查個仆街校長有無精神壓逼老師<br />\n希望更多李東海小學老師挺身爆料俾傳媒，一定要推出搵出真相<br />\n將呢啲仆街學校「土皇帝」拉落嚟！！！<br />\n<br />\n如果東華三院唔徹查，還林老師一個公道，本人呼籲連登仔唔好捐錢俾東華，亦要叫身邊嘅親朋戚友咪撚捐！！！<br />\n<br />\n希望蘋果繼續推，詳細報道：<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">【獨家】最後上課日程曝光 李東海小學老師墮斃前夕遭校長照肺爆喊</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190308/59347174\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190308%2F59347174&d=i2Kzi6k%2Bo1XjTd2IKJX6uZriIWEbfV0cuvPRs67P9cA%3D&h=dfa93003\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190308%2F59347174&h=7e428741\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190308/59347174</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>【獨家】李東海教師墮樓前夕被鬧原因曝光：校長不滿「悔過書」內容令重寫</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190309/59349758\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190309%2F59349758&d=i2Kzi6k%2Bo1XjTd2IKJX6uZriIWEbfV0cuvPRs67P9cA%3D&h=3122108e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190309%2F59349758&h=15a42a5c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190309/59349758</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>【獨家】李東海小學教師兩投訴校長態度專橫 東華僅索書面解釋了事</strong></span><br />\n<a href=